quran[9{c,v,t}:
10,34,( un se ) pucho ke bhala tumhare sharikon mein se koi aisa hai ke makhlooq ko abtdan peda kere ( aur ) phir is ko dobarah banaye? keh do ke khuda hi pehli baar peda karta hai phir wohi is ko dobarah peda kere ga to tum kahan uksay jarahay ho
10,35,pucho ke bhala tumahray sharikon mein kon aisa hai ke haq ka rasta dukhaay. keh do ke khuda hi haq ka rasta dekhata hai. bhala jo haq ka rasta dukhaay woh is qabil hai ke uss ki pairwi ki jaye ya woh ke jab taq koi usay rasta nah betaye rasta nah paye. to tum kokiya howa hai kaisa insaaf karte ho ?
10,36,aur un mein se aksar sirf zan ki pairwi karte hain. aur kuch shak nahi ke zan haq ke muqablay mein kuch bhi kaar amad nahi ho sakta. be shak khuda tumahray ( sab ) af-aal se waaqif hai
10,37,aur yeh quran aisa nahi ke khuda ke siwa koi is ko apni taraf se bana laaye. haan ( haan yeh khuda ka kalaam hai ) jo ( kitaaben ) is se pehlay ( ki ) hain. un ki tasdeeq karta hai aur un hi kitabon ki ( is mein ) tafseel hai is mein kuch shak nahi ( ke ) yeh rab alameen ki taraf se ( nazil howa ) hai
10,38,kiya yeh log kehte hain ke paighambar ne is ko apni taraf se bana liya hai keh do ke agar sachey ho to tum bhi is terhan ki aik sourat bana lao aur khuda ke siwa jin ko tum bulaa sakuu bulaa bhi lau
10,39,haqeeqat yeh hai ke jis cheez ke ilm par yeh qaboo nahi paske is ko ( nadani se ) jhutla diya aur abhi is ki haqeeqat un par khuli hi nahi. isi terhan jo log un se pehlay they unhon ne takzieeb ki thi so dekh lau zaalmon ka injaam kaisa howa
10,40,aur un mein se kuch to aisay hain ke is par imaan le atay hain aur kuch aisay hain ke imaan nahi laatay. aur tumahra perwar-digaar shariron se khoob waaqif hai
10,41,aur agar yeh tumhari takzieeb karen to keh do ke mujh ko mere aamaal ( ka badla miley ga ) aur tum ko tumahray aamaal ( ka ) tum mere amlon ka jawab da nahi ho aur mein tumahray amlon ka jawabdeh nahi hon
10,42,aur un mein se baaz aisay hain ke tumhari taraf kaan lagatay hain tokiya tum behroon ko sunaaoo ge agarchay kuch bhi ( suntay ) samajte nah hon
